<div class='row'>
<div class='col-lg-3'>
<a class='talk-learnmore ga-link' data-ga-action='click' data-ga-category='talk.extras' data-ga-label='learnMore:from_the_blog|http://ideas.ted.com/2014/08/14/5-basic-skills-of-power/' href='http://ideas.ted.com/2014/08/14/5-basic-skills-of-power/' target='_blank'>
<i class="icon icon_arrow-alt-right learnmore_arrow" title="Arrow"></i><span class="screen-reader-text">Arrow</span>
<div class='h9 talk-learnmore__title m4'>How you too can influence change</div>
<div class='talk-learnmore__dek'><p>Eric Liu reveals his five basic skills of power and shows how anyone can use them to make a difference.</p>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col-lg-3'>
<a class='talk-learnmore ga-link' data-ga-action='click' data-ga-category='talk.extras' data-ga-label='learnMore:from_the_blog|http://www.tedcity2.org/about/' href='http://www.tedcity2.org/about/' target='_blank'>
<i class="icon icon_arrow-alt-right learnmore_arrow" title="Arrow"></i><span class="screen-reader-text">Arrow</span>
<div class='h9 talk-learnmore__title m4'>The city of the future</div>
<div class='talk-learnmore__dek'><p>What's next for our urban spaces? Explore TEDCity2.0, a site born from the 2012 TED Prize wish that paints a complex picture of the future city — a safer, healthier, more playful and more beautiful place for all.</p>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col-lg-3'>
<a class='talk-learnmore ga-link' data-ga-action='click' data-ga-category='talk.extras' data-ga-label='learnMore:from_the_blog|http://ed.ted.com/lessons/how-to-understand-power-eric-liu' href='http://ed.ted.com/lessons/how-to-understand-power-eric-liu' target='_blank'>
